1 by default, mock files should appear in the directory where pegomock is run.
2 by default, their package name should be the same as the current package + _test, not of the interface's package.
3 if only an interface is specified (i.e., if no package is specified), the current package is assumed as the source
4 to avoid ambiguouity, only one interface per cli run can be specified
5 there's parameter for the output package defaulting to 2
6 param for the output file
